Don't we require a bachelor's degree?

23
00:02:19,557 --> 00:02:20,433
I apologize.

24
00:02:20,516 --> 00:02:23,061
There must've been a mistake
during the resume screening process.

25
00:02:32,487 --> 00:02:34,197
Hello, I am interviewee number 511,

26
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,448
Cheon Sa-rang.

27
00:02:36,741 --> 00:02:40,036
2015 KING HOTEL TRAINEESHIP INTERVIEW

28
00:02:57,678 --> 00:02:59,055
Your hobby is playing the piano.

29
